Comment: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:32.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,その腕に絡んだ時計の針は
Comment: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:33.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:38.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,狂わないなんて信じていないで
Comment: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,進もうと急かすような秒針
Comment: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:46.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Close-set mind
Comment: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:51.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,巻き戻そう 抓んだ竜頭回し
Comment: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:55.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇想夢譚になっていく
Comment: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:58.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,曖昧が依然あるなら
Comment: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,触れて確かめてしまえばいいよ
Comment: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:04.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,現実を脱がせて
Comment: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:07.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let me hightail it out of here
Comment: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:10.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,繰り返すほど牴牾しい
Comment: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:17.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,儚いって知りながら 求めてしまう
Comment: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,背徳の夢
Comment: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:32.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,纏繞在你腕上的時針
Comment: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:38.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,毋庸置疑會行至瘋狂
Comment: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,彷彿在催促前行的秒針
Comment: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:51.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,擰動發條 讓我們逆轉時光吧
Comment: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:55.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,墜入夢幻奇譚
Comment: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:58.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,若曖昧仍舊存在
Comment: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:01.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,親自觸碰來確認這一切
Comment: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:04.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,褪去現實的桎梏
Comment: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:10.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,越是重演便越顯矛盾
Comment: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:17.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,明知虛幻 卻仍執於追尋
Comment: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,這場背德之夢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------STAFF----------
